ky啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T20:15:31.000Z","msg":"你再激你呀爸既話 我而家就摑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63acfa39fba8c9b5885c6f7d305310209a8be0aa","tid":569180,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:16:15.000Z","msg":"物以類聚<br />\n人以群分<br />\n<br />\n道不同不相為謀<br />\n<br />\n正如好多撚樣豉油打做鼓油<br />\nsteam打做stream<br />\n<br />\n你咪當佢戇鳩遠離佢囉"},{"pid":"219234684562ed0507339865b266d478584ec0a1","tid":569180,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc0f5bde7db47febe952bd0a7c1ea39893f786d1","tid":569180,"uid":77143,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"db600c4866f0fb769d42825b8e241850450505b1","tid":569180,"uid":162564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"識人見到汽水裝喺香檳樽裏面都叫香檳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:26:08.000Z","msg":"我將忌簾裝係一個磨砂香檳樽入面<br />\n我就唔撚信你識分<br />\n唔准掂只准望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:42:19.000Z","msg":"香檳冇咁黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一睇就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你裝落Dom樽就睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dd47684b97e4988669ff6fdbefb11968f886e6","tid":569180,"uid":90023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:13:31.000Z","msg":"咁唔係飲開酒 唔識好出奇咩<br />\n<br />\n見到有氣酒 叫 香檳 都好常見<br />\n但你唔識咪教人囉<br />\n<br />\n香檳 只係法國入面一個地區 <br />\n係香檳區 (champagne) 出產既 sparkling wine 先可以叫champagne<br />\n<br />\n而法國入面仲有其他地區都會出產 sparkling wine... 佢地叫 cremant<br />\n例如有 Loire Valley, Bourgogne, Alsace.... <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://winefolly.com/review/cremant-wine/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwinefolly.com%2Freview%2Fcremant-wine%2F&d=jy%2FSht6CnzJSEoys9N7VJ9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=aba37918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://winefolly.com/review/cremant-wine/</a><br />\n<br />\nDetails 可以睇上面條link<br />\n<br />\n除左法國有出產sparkling wine .. 意大利都有prosecco 西班牙有cava... 同埋 new world 例如 澳洲 new zealand 都有sparkling wines 出產"}]}